  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation of the kernel</title>

    <xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2003/XInclude"
    href="../../bootable/x86/kernel.xml"
    xpointer="xpointer(id('install-kernel')/para[1])"/>

    <para>Prepare for compilation by running the following command:</para>

<screen><userinput>make mrproper ARCH=sparc64 CROSS_COMPILE=${LFS_TARGET}-</userinput></screen>

    <xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2003/XInclude"
    href="../../bootable/x86/kernel.xml"
    xpointer="xpointer(id('install-kernel')/para[3])"/>

    <xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2003/XInclude"
    href="../x86/kernel.xml"
    xpointer="xpointer(//*[@role='installation']/para[4])"/>

    <xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2003/XInclude"
    href="../x86/kernel.xml"
    xpointer="xpointer(//*[@role='installation']/screen[2])"/>

    <para>Configure the kernel via a menu-driven interface:</para>

<screen><userinput>make ARCH=sparc64 CROSS_COMPILE=${LFS_TARGET}- menuconfig</userinput></screen>

    <para>Alternatively, <command>make ARCH=sparc64 CROSS_COMPILE=${LFS_TARGET}-
    oldconfig</command> may be more appropriate in some situations. See the
    <filename>README</filename> file for more information.</para>

    <xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2003/XInclude"
    href="../../bootable/x86/kernel.xml"
    xpointer="xpointer(id('install-kernel')/note[1])"/>

    <xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2003/XInclude"
    href="../../bootable/x86/kernel.xml"
    xpointer="xpointer(id('install-kernel')/para[9])"/>

    <xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2003/XInclude"
    href="../../bootable/x86/kernel.xml"
    xpointer="xpointer(id('install-kernel')/para[10])"/>

    <xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2003/XInclude"
    href="../../bootable/x86/kernel.xml"
    xpointer="xpointer(id('install-kernel')/para[11])"/>

    <xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2003/XInclude"
    href="../../bootable/x86/kernel.xml"
    xpointer="xpointer(id('install-kernel')/note[2])"/>

    <para>Compile the kernel image and modules:</para>

<screen><userinput>make ARCH=sparc64 CROSS_COMPILE=${LFS_TARGET}-</userinput></screen>

    <xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2003/XInclude"
    href="../x86/kernel.xml"
    xpointer="xpointer(//*[@role='installation']/para[11])"/>

    <xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2003/XInclude"
    href="../../bootable/x86/kernel.xml"
    xpointer="xpointer(id('install-kernel')/para[14])"/>

    <xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2003/XInclude"
    href="../../bootable/x86/kernel.xml"
    xpointer="xpointer(id('install-kernel')/screen[5])"/>

    <xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2003/XInclude"
    href="../../bootable/x86/kernel.xml"
    xpointer="xpointer(id('install-kernel')/para[15])"/>

    <xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2003/XInclude"
    href="../../bootable/x86/kernel.xml"
    xpointer="xpointer(id('install-kernel')/para[16])"/>

<screen><userinput>make INSTALL_MOD_PATH=${LFS} ARCH=sparc64 \
   CROSS_COMPILE=${LFS_TARGET}- modules_install</userinput></screen>

    <xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2003/XInclude"
    href="../../bootable/x86/kernel.xml"
    xpointer="xpointer(id('install-kernel')/para[17])"/>

    <xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2003/XInclude"
    href="../x86/kernel.xml"
    xpointer="xpointer(//*[@role='installation']/para[16])"/>

    <para>Issue the following command to install the kernel:</para>

<screen><userinput>cp vmlinux ${LFS}/boot/lfskernel-&linux-sparc64-version;</userinput></screen>

    <xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2003/XInclude"
    href="../../bootable/x86/kernel.xml"
    xpointer="xpointer(id('install-kernel')/para[20])"/>

<screen><userinput>cp System.map ${LFS}/boot/System.map-&linux-sparc64-version;</userinput></screen>

    <xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2003/XInclude"
    href="../../bootable/x86/kernel.xml"
    xpointer="xpointer(id('install-kernel')/para[21])"/>

<screen><userinput>cp .config ${LFS}/boot/config-&linux-sparc64-version;</userinput></screen>

    <xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2003/XInclude"
    href="../../bootable/x86/kernel.xml"
    xpointer="xpointer(id('install-kernel')/para[22])"/>

    <xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2003/XInclude"
    href="../../bootable/sparc64/kernel.xml"
    xpointer="xpointer(//*[@role='installation']/para[24])"/>

    <xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2003/XInclude"
    href="../../bootable/x86/kernel.xml"
    xpointer="xpointer(id('install-kernel')/warning[1])"/>

